I did manage to get free though but took some timing and a guildies help. A porter wouldn't due to faction and time issues of port cast time so what I did was get another bard at the dock and when I zoned in we formed a group and moment the boat was just as the boat was coming to the dock he hit his MMM song took two pulses but managed to knock me free and lucked out that he didn't get caught as well.
<br />

