This was changed long ago when people on the PvP servers complained that a bard was able to freely attack players using the boats to move about the world.  So instead of Sony adjusting this to affect bards on those servers, I had to learn my instruments standing around or in combat usage.  I guess bards can move and cast ~spells~, unless they are on a boat.
<br />

<br />
Do the boats even work?  Bristlebane has those little folks sending everyone off.
<br />
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Axlrose - ...&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</span></td>
